        "description": "We should add a {{take}}\u00a0method to {{Array/ChunkedArray/Column}}\u00a0that takes a list of indices and returns a reordered array.\r\n\r\nFor reference, see Pandas' interface: https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/blob/2cbdd9a2cd19501c98582490e35c5402ae6de941/pandas/core/arrays/base.py#L466",
        "customfield_10010": null,
